  "siteName": "CSDN",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">编译 | 苏宓</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:normal;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">出品 | CSDN（ID：CSDNnews）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 辅助编码工具的流行，已经让不少程序员的写代码习惯发生了巨大变化。那么，这会不会影响到他们使用编程语言的频率？最新的数据告诉我们：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">会的。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">近日，IEEE Spectrum 发布了年度“顶级编程语言”榜单，这已经是他们连续第 12 年发布这份排名。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">结果显示，Python 依旧是当之无愧的王者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Spectrum 总榜单</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">中（根据 IEEE 成员兴趣加权），Python 在过去十年里</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;p1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">已经连续拿下十次 Spectrum 总榜首，这次也并不例外，其</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">继续稳坐第一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">今年榜单变化最大的要属 JavaScript 了，它从去年的第三名跌到今年的第六名。要知道，JavaScript 一直是网页开发的“当家花旦”，而现在它的相对热度下降，很可能和 AI 工具在网页开发上的渗透有关。毕竟随着“Vibe Coding”（氛围编程）的流行，它常被很多技术人、爱好者用来做网页开发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100339181\" data-ratio=\"1.4138461538461538\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"650\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09df762b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq7kM1wTg0ehdiaPp2YVqiaGUlx3hb2JbOvMoYzQYCFNGyFID3IYyeHZEosIGfDdKoIicw9InicAtobbJ8g9icAHYgvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在&nbsp;</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“Jobs”榜单</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（更关注雇主实际需求）中，Python 也迎来了里程碑式的突破：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">首次拿下第一，把 SQL 挤到第二。</span>虽然如此，SQL 技能在简历上依然是超级加分项，雇主仍然很看重。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100339183\" data-ratio=\"1.4092307692307693\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"650\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf972dde&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq7kM1wTg0ehdiaPp2YVqiaGUlx3hb2JbOv3meTAKSYvwf31Dfvvk0a0GA5LwCBVXWjnfNOq01Sogo2r2UX8bJib2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果回顾历史走势，榜单的变化就更有意思了。最早排名时，Java、C、C++ 和 Python 几乎不分伯仲。2016 年，C 曾一度超越 Java，而 Python 则是在 2017 年才登顶。当时几大语言的分数都还紧紧咬住。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">可如今，差距拉开了：2024 年的 Spectrum 榜单里，Python 得分是 1，Java 只有 0.4986，差距比十年前明显大得多。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一些老牌语言也逐渐淡出。比如 Matlab，2014/2015 年还能排到前十，今年则掉到第 20 位，指数从当年的 0.724 掉到 0.0957。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从整体数据来看，今年有 19 种语言在 Spectrum 榜单上的指数超过 0.1，而去年只有 15 种；在职位需求榜单上，能超过 0.1 的则只有 13 种。年度变化中，JavaScript 是跌幅最大的，从 0.4451 掉到 0.2872。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在 Trending 榜单上，Python 依旧遥遥领先，Java 排在第二（0.6777），C++ 位列第三（0.4458），差距依然很明显。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100339182\" data-ratio=\"1.4144838212634823\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"649\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3b40c873&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq7kM1wTg0ehdiaPp2YVqiaGUlx3hb2JbOv2R5ov7l62a9bficJECicwWibicAlfzrn8Mltf0nI8PNBGVpenK4TSlsevw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后再说说榜单的来源。和往年一样，IEEE 这份排名结合了多种渠道的数据，包括 Google 搜索、GitHub 活跃度、IEEE Xplore 论文数量，以及 IEEE Career Builder 的职位数据。不同榜单权重不同，其中“职位需求”榜最直观，也最贴近就业市场。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过对于这种趋势，IEEE 官方也解读道：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">如今的程序员对这些公开指标的依赖正在减少。他们不再翻书或在 Stack Exchange 上搜索答案，而是会在私下与 LLM（如 Claude 或 ChatGPT）聊天。在 Cursor 等 AI 助手的帮助下，编程过程中需要提问的情况大幅减少。例如，在 TPL 评估的所有语言中，2025 年每周在 Stack Exchange 发布的问题数量仅为 2024 年的 22%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">公开指标信号的减弱，使得跨语言的流行度追踪变得更加困难。解决这一问题的方法包括寻找新的指标，或者尝试直接调查程序员——无论他们的背景和偏好如何。然而，更根本的问题正在悄然出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">无论是资深程序员用 AI 完成重复劳动，还是新手用 vibe 编程完成一个完整的 Web 应用，AI 的辅助都意味着程序员对具体编程语言的关注越来越少。从语法细节，到流程控制、函数设计，再到程序整体结构，越来越多的工作被交给 AI 来处理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IEEE 认为 AI 辅助工具的普及，会带来一个显而易见的长期后果——<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">新语言的出现可能会变得更加困难。</span>过去，一个新语言往往从个人或小团队的想法开始，靠着不停推广，慢慢吸引贡献者和用户。但在今天，很多人已经在质疑：未来的编程语言，还会像过去那样发展吗？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">其表示，要回答这个问题，得先回头看看编程语言的初心。现代高级语言的核心使命，其实就两件事：</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">帮程序员更方便地处理数据</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，以及</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">防止程序员自己犯蠢</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">这两个目标都不是新鲜事。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">早在 Fortran 和 Cobol 时代，语言就开始为科学计算和商业数据处理提供抽象层；而后来 Dijkstra 在 1968 年的一篇论文里掀起一场：“别再随便用 Go To 了”运动——理由是这样会写出一坨“意大利面条代码”，别人根本看不懂。事实证明，他的观点最终胜出，如今大多数语言里 Go To 基本都被“消灭”，取而代之的是更规整的函数、循环和模块。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">但有趣的是，这些结构在 CPU 层面根本不存在。Arm、x86、RISC-V 的指令集里，程序的流程控制只有三种：条件跳转、无条件跳转、以及带返回的跳转。换句话说，所谓的结构化编程，最后都还是“Go To”。数据类型也一样，看似严谨，其实在内存里不过是些比特流。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">这就引出了一个问题：</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">如果 AI 编程助手足够强大，还需要这些抽象和保护机制吗？</span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">一些研究已经给出了有趣的答案。普林斯顿的团队搞出了一个叫&nbsp;</span></b><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">Dall-EM</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">&nbsp;的生成式 AI，可以直接设计射频和电磁滤波器。过去这类设计几乎是“黑魔法”，要靠专家反复调试，而 Dall-EM 却能从输入和输出直接生成类似二维码的结构，人类工程师想都想不到，却能跑得很好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">类比到编程领域，未来 AI 会不会直接跳过“人类可读的高级语言”，把提示词翻译成中间语言，再交给编译器跑起来？<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">对人类来说，代码可能就是个黑盒，但依旧能模块化、能测试、能验证质量。到那时候，程序员的日常也许不是改 bug，而是改提示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">不过，这并不意味着程序员会被彻底取代。真正需要人来拍板的，依旧是</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">架构设计和算法选择</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">：路径规划该用 A* 还是新方法？模块要怎么和大系统对接？这些都是 AI 很难全权决定的。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">换句话说，未来更值钱的，不是写多少行代码，而是能不能理解底层逻辑、做好系统设计。</span>相比“速成班”学语言，计算机科学的基础功反而会变得更重要。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">基于此，IEEE 自己也提出了一个自问自答式的问题：那 2026 年还会有“最流行编程语言”排行榜吗？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">其官方给出的回答是：编程正经历自 20 世纪 50 年代编译器诞生以来最大的一次变革。就算有人唱衰 AI 是泡沫，但历史告诉我们，每一次泡沫都会沉淀出几样真正能用的东西。而 AI 写代码，大概率就是其中之一。所以未来一年，在编程语言榜单上，我们可能需要重新思考：“流行度”该怎么算？还要不要看搜索量和招聘需求，还是干脆看哪种提示词在 AI 工具里最常用？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">那么，在你看来，在 AI 时代，</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">什么才算一门“流行语言”？</span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://spectrum.ieee.org/top-programming-languages-2025\" target=\"_blank\">https://spectrum.ieee.org/top-programming-languages-2025</a></span></span></b></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章揭示了 IEEE Spectrum 2025 年编程语言榜单，Python 持续称王，并深入探讨了 AI 辅助编码对编程语言流行度、开发者核心能力及未来语言发展模式的深远影响。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章揭示了 IEEE Spectrum 2025 年编程语言榜单，Python 持续称王，并深入探讨了 AI 辅助编码对编程语言流行度、开发者核心能力及未来语言发展模式的深远影响。",
  "summary": "文章首先发布了 IEEE Spectrum 2025 年度顶级编程语言榜单，指出 Python 连续十年稳居总榜首，并在“Jobs”榜单中首次超越 SQL 位列第一，凸显其在 AI 时代的主导地位。JavaScript 则出现明显下滑，可能与 AI 在网页开发中的渗透有关。文章随后回顾了历史榜单变化，强调了 Python 与 Java 等老牌语言差距的拉大。最核心的部分在于深入分析了 AI 辅助编码工具的普及对编程领域带来的变革。作者指出，AI 工具的广泛应用正在减少程序员对传统指标（如 Stack Exchange 搜索）的依赖，并可能改变新语言的诞生和发展模式。未来的编程可能从高级语言直接转向 AI 生成中间语言，程序员的核心价值将更多体现在底层逻辑理解和系统架构设计上，而非具体代码编写。文章最后探讨了在 AI 时代，“流行语言”定义可能需要重新思考，预示着编程领域将迎来编译器诞生以来最大的变革。",
